source: TEXT_CMNDEFTEMPORARYBAG_00083_TALK_ACTOR_01<tab>Well met, friend. I am in charge of storing property lost during the Calamity.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFTEMPORARYBAG_00083_TALK_ACTOR_01<tab>Salut, <var 08 E905 ((ma)) ((mon)) /var> jeune ami<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>. Je me charge de retourner les objets perdus lors du Fléau à leurs pro<var 16 /var>prié<var 16 /var>taires.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFTEMPORARYBAG_00083_TALK_Q1<tab>Are you here to reclaim your belongings?

target: TEXT_CMNDEFTEMPORARYBAG_00083_TALK_A2<tab>En savoir plus sur les objets perdus

source: TEXT_CMNDEFTEMPORARYBAG_00083_TALK_ACTOR_05<tab>Countless souls went missing during the Calamity, and a veritable mountain of articles was left ownerless. The Adventurers' Guild has been holding such articles in safekeeping in hopes that their owners will one day reclaim them.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFTEMPORARYBAG_00083_TALK_ACTOR_05<tab>Un grand nombre de personnes ont disparu sans laisser de trace, mais en abandonnant des montagnes de biens lors du Fléau. La guilde des aventuriers conserve ces possessions en espérant que leurs pro<var 16 /var>prié<var 16 /var>taires viendront les réclamer.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFTEMPORARYBAG_00083_TALK_ACTOR_06<tab>Please be warned, however, that we are <var 1A 02 /var>not<var 1A 01 /var> a storage service. The items you retrieve become your sole responsibility, and cannot be returned to us under any circumstance.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFTEMPORARYBAG_00083_TALK_ACTOR_06<tab>Je tiens toutefois à souligner le fait que nous ne sommes pas pour autant un service de consigne. Si vous récupérez des objets, nous ne les reprendrons en aucun cas.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFTEMPORARYBAG_00083_TALK_ACTOR_10<tab>Fewer folk come forward to reclaim their belongings with each passing day.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFTEMPORARYBAG_00083_TALK_ACTOR_10<tab>Le nombre d'aventuriers venant récupérer des objets perdus diminue de jour en jour.

source: TEXT_CMNDEFTEMPORARYBAG_00083_TALK_ACTOR_11<tab>It saddens me to think that some items will remain in our safekeeping forever, their owners never to return.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFTEMPORARYBAG_00083_TALK_ACTOR_11<tab>Cela me chagrine de savoir que certains de ces biens ne reverront sans doute jamais leurs pro<var 16 /var>prié<var 16 /var>taires.
